{"lemma":"نَظَراتٌ","slug":"نَظَراتٌ","root":"ن.ظ.ر","root_slug":"ن-ظ-ر","root_link":"/words/roots/ن-ظ-ر","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"نَظْرَة","root":"نظر","pos":"N","occurrence_count":1},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n40046","n40047"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%86%D9%8E%D8%B8%D9%8E%D8%B1%D8%A7%D8%AA%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"instance noun of نَظَرَ (naẓara): a look","examples":[{"text":"أَلْقَى نَظْرَةً","english":"he had a look"}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"perspective"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n40046","headword_ar":"نَظْرَةٌ","root":"nZr","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A look: a quick look or glance:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naZaraAtN","text_ar":"نَظَرَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (A.) Hence the trad.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA tutobiEi Aln~aTorapa","text_ar":"لَا تُتْبِعِ النَّطْرَةَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aln~aZorapa faA_in~a laka AlA^uwolaY walayosato laka AlA=xirapu","text_ar":"النَّظْرَةَ فَاـِنَّ لَكَ الاُوْلَى وَلَيْسَتْ لَكَ الا=خِرَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Thou shalt not make a look to follow a look; for the former is thine"},{"kind":"text","text":"or right,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lad the latter is not thine:"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e., when thou hast once looked at anything forbidden, unintentionally, thou shalt not look at it a second time]. (T, TA.) And the saying of a certain wise man,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mano lamo taEomalo","text_ar":"مَنْ لَمْ تَعْمَلْ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naZoratuhu lamo yaEomalo lisaAnuhu","text_ar":"نَظْرَتُهُ لَمْ يَعْمَلْ لِسَانُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He whose look does not produce an effect, his tongue does not produce an effect"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; (T;) meaning, that he who is not restrained from a fault or offence by being looked at is not restrained by speech. (TA.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A stroke of an"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"evil"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"eye:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a stroke of an"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"evil"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"eye by which one is affected from the jinn's looking at him;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, S; *) as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"safoEapN","text_ar":"سَفْعَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (T;) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a touch,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a slight taint"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"infection of insanity."},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaAy^ifN","text_ar":"طَايِفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":",)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from the jinn:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a swoon."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An alteration of the body"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"complexion by emaciation"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hunger"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"travel"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c. (S, M, K.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Foulness; ugliness:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(AA, TA:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"evilness;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"badness, of form"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"appearance; a fault: a defect; an imperfection."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K.) ―         -b5-  (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Reverence, veneration, awe,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fear,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(I Aar, T, K,) ―         -b6-  (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Compassion, pity, merry."},{"kind":"text","text":"(I Aar, T, K,)"}],"source_refs":["T","TA","AA"]},{"entry_id":"n40047","headword_ar":"نَظِرَةٌ","root":"nZr","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A postponement; a delay."},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, S, M, Msb, K.) It is said in the Kur. [ii. 280.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fanaZrapN A_ilaY mayosarapK","text_ar":"فَنَظرَةٌ اـِلَى مَيْسَرَةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Then"},{"kind":"text","text":"let there be"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a postponement,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"delay, until"},{"kind":"text","text":"he shall be in"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an easy state of circumstances"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; (T, M, Msb) a. c.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faA_inoZaArN","text_ar":"فَاـِنْظَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (T,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fataA^oxiyrN","text_ar":"فَتَاْخِيرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Msb) and accord. to another reading, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fanaAZirapN","text_ar":"فَنَاظِرَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kaA*ibapN","text_ar":"كَاذِبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in the Kur, lvi. 2. (M.) You say also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baAEa minohu Al$~aYo'a binaZirapK","text_ar":"بَاعَ مِنْهُ الشَّىْءَ بِنَظِرَةٍ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He sold to him the thing with postponement of the payment, he sold to him the thing upon credit."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ai$otarayotuhu minohu binaZirapK","text_ar":"اِشْتَرَيْتُهُ مِنْهُ بِنَظِرَةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biA_inoZaArK","text_ar":"بِاـِنْظَارٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I bought a of him with postponement of the payment; I bought a of him upon credit."},{"kind":"text","text":"(T.)"}],"source_refs":["T","M","Msb"]}]}}